# Owners

## Overview

The Owners page provides full CRUD management of Owner records. An Owner is a user with elevated (admin-level) access who can own one or more companies. Only the site Admin can access this page.

## Access

| Role       | Access                                      |
| ---------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| Admin      | Full access — create, edit, delete owners   |
| All others | Redirected away (via `SysadminRoute` guard) |

## Table Columns

| Column       | Description                                                      |
| ------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Name         | Owner's first + last name (from their linked user record)        |
| Email        | Owner's email address                                            |
| Display Name | Optional business/public display name                            |
| Tax ID       | Optional tax identifier                                          |
| Status       | `active`, `suspended`, or `inactive` — shown as a coloured badge |
| Created      | Date the owner record was created                                |
| Actions      | **Edit** · **Delete** (pinned right, non-resizable)              |

## Actions

### New Owner

Opens **CreateOwnerModal** — a form requiring:

- First name, Last name
- Email, Password (min 8 characters)
- Display Name _(optional)_
- Tax ID _(optional)_

On creation a new `User` record (`role = admin`) and an `Owner` record are created atomically in a single transaction.

### Edit Owner

Opens **EditOwnerModal** — allows updating name, email, phone, address, display name, tax ID, and owner status.

### Delete Owner

Opens **DeleteOwnerModal** — a confirmation dialog. Deletion is permanent and will also remove the linked user account.

## Files

| File                   | Purpose                                                              |
| ---------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `Owners.tsx`           | Main page component — AG Grid table, modal orchestration             |
| `Owners.columns.tsx`   | AG Grid column definitions including status badge and action buttons |
| `CreateOwnerModal.tsx` | Form modal for creating a new owner (uses `react-hook-form`)         |
| `EditOwnerModal.tsx`   | Form modal for editing an existing owner                             |
| `DeleteOwnerModal.tsx` | Confirmation modal for deleting an owner                             |
